data.title: Kobe Bryant GPT Agent
data.meta_description: Hi, I'm agent Kobe Bryant. Ask me questions such as "When and where was Kobe Bryant born?" or "Who is Kobe Bryant?".
data.text:
When did Kobe Bryant become the first player in NBA history to achieve 47 points, eight rebounds, five assists, four blocks, and three steals in a game?

What are Kobe Bryant's career averages in points, rebounds, assists, and steals per game?

What was Kobe Bryant's middle name and how did he get it?

How many seasons did Kobe Bryant play in the NBA?
